nodes.text: Chay Tebbic was a female Sullustan who worked as a bartender in the Cantina Oceana in Dorumaa City on Dorumaa. After she had worked there for several years, she witnessed a fight between Echari Di'San and Rysko Barnt in the cantina. Barnt was murdered shortly afterward, and Tebbic called the authorities to inform them of the crime.
